<se_def>Cash: So this is it, huh? The place where you can listen to the oh-so-wise words of great Goldings past.
<se_def>Cash: But now that I'm here, I don't have a clue what I'm supposed to do next. Man! I wish I'd listened to Dad more carefully.
<se_high>Carrie: You know, I figured the markings on the stone were going to be an inscription from our ancestors. Guess I was wrong.
